    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6 and boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>Fable pulled mushrooms</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until lightly browned</p>",
