    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong> into thin wedges</p><p>Chop your<strong> sweet</strong> <strong>potato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p>",
